---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-radar-border)] bg-[var(--color-radar-surface)] mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-4">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-radar-bg)] border border-[var(--color-radar-border)] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[var(--color-radar-accent)]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke-dasharray="3 3" opacity="0.6"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-[var(--color-radar-text)]">Free AI Radar</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
          Novedades de inteligencia artificial gratis, filtradas y analizadas críticamente. Sin directorios interminables y sin humo publicitario.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-radar-text)] mb-4 font-sora">Navegación</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5">
          <a href="/" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">Inicio</a>
          <a href="/tools" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">Herramientas</a>
          <a href="/creators" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">Creadores</a>
          <a href="/comfyui-sin-gpu" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">ComfyUI sin GPU</a>
          <a href="/noticias" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">Noticias IA</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-radar-text)] mb-4 font-sora">Metodología e Info</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5">
          <a href="/methodology" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">Cómo puntuamos</a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">Sobre el proyecto</a>
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-xs text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-radar-accent)] transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none">Privacidad</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--color-radar-border)] flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-center sm:text-left text-[10px] text-[var(--color-radar-text-muted)]">
      <div>
        &copy; {currentYear} Free AI Radar. Datos recopilados y analizados de forma independiente.
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-md sm:text-right">
        No garantizamos la exactitud permanente de los planes de terceros — verifique siempre en el sitio oficial correspondiente.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
